results.name: Triangle read by rows: T(n,d) is the number of distinct properly d-dimensional polyominoes (or polycubes) with n cells (n >= 1, d >= 0).
link: W. F. Lunnon, Counting multidimensional polyominoes. Computer Journal 18 (1975), no. 4, pp. 366-367.
xref: Row sums give A005519. Columns give A006765, A006766, A006767, A006768.
A000055 is first diagonal; A036364 is second diagonal.
Cf. A330891 (cumulative sums of the rows).
results.author: Richard C. Schroeppel
